author: zhaobenny
hollowstrawberry
description: Enables the generation of Stable Diffusion images in Discord using a provided AUTOMATIC1111 stable-diffusion-webui endpoint
install_msg:
This cog will require an AUTOMATIC1111-like endpoint with API mode enabled. (See cog `README.md`)
You must set an endpoint URL using the `endpoint` command in either `[p]aimage` or `[p]aimageowner`
Slash commands are **highly recommended** , enable via `[p]slash enablecog aimage`, then `[p]slash sync`
short: A1111 Stable Diffusion image generation in Discord
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not persistently store data or metadata about users.
